# Fashion, Home + Interiors Color Specifier Replacement Page - Pantone Color of the Year 2022

## Formatted for use in Pantone FHI Color Specifier books

Sku#: 17-3938PAGE

$ 11.00

Add To Cart

Keep your Fashion, Home + Interiors (FHI) Color Specifier up to date with a full page of the new Pantone Color of the Year for 2022. PANTONE® 17-3938 Very Peri is a dynamic periwinkle blue hue with a vivifying violet-red undertone that blends the faithfulness and constancy of blue with the energy and excitement of red. Designers and decision makers can use the removable paper chips for mood board and palette development, specifying on product sketches, communicating color to clients, or bringing along to stores.

- Update your FHI Color Specifier books with the new Pantone Color of the Year 2022
- Chips offer shareable, versatile color for inspiration, color communication, and quality control

